40:39.011 --> 40:41.354
<i>come to an end on Oak Island.</i>

40:41.513 --> 40:44.849
<i>And even though Rick, Marty,
Craig, and their team</i>

40:44.942 --> 40:48.936
<i>still struggle to decode
the mystery of the Money Pit,</i>

40:49.021 --> 40:53.191
<i>the discoveries that they keep
